  "title": "Codex 与 Anydocs 的协作方式",
  "description": "把 Codex 放在 MCP 驱动的文档工作流里。",
  "tags": [
    "codex",
    "workflow"
  ],
  "status": "published",
  "updatedAt": "2026-04-02T00:00:00.000Z",
  "content": {
    "version": 1,
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "id": "block-1",
        "level": 1,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Codex 与 Anydocs 的协作方式"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "在 Anydocs 里，Codex 最适合做的是："
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "id": "block-3",
        "style": "bulleted",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "element-3-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "先用 `project_open` 读取项目 contract"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-4-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "查看 `project_open.authoring` 里的 templates、resources 和 metadataSchema"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-5-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "需要完整流程时读取 `anydocs://authoring/guidance`"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-6-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "先读取页面现状，再决定 create 还是 update"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-7-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "之后通过 `page_create_from_template`、`page_create` 或 `page_update` 做可解释的变更"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-8-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "最后再用 `page_set_status` 推进页面状态"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "element-9-item-1",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "导航改动使用 MCP 导航工具，而不是手工重写 JSON"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "id": "block-10",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "关键点不是让 Codex 直接改 `pages/*.json`，而是让它始终通过 MCP 工具操作。"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
